{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"File.File()","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/File/File","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/File\"><code>File</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><em><code>File()</code></em></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>属性</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/File/lastModified\"><code>lastModified</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/File/lastModifiedDate\"><code>lastModifiedDate</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/File/name\"><code>name</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/File/type\"><code>type</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/File/webkitRelativePath\"><code>webkitRelativePath</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>继承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Blob\"><code>Blob</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p><code><strong>File()</strong></code>&nbsp;构造器创建新的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/File\"><code>File</code></a> 对象实例。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">var myFile = new File(bits, name[, options]);</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参数","title":"参数","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"bits\"><em>bits</em></dt>\n <dd>一个包含<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer\"><code>ArrayBuffer</code></a>，<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/TypedArray\"><code>ArrayBufferView</code></a>，<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Blob\"><code>Blob</code></a>，或者&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a> 对象的&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Array\"><code>Array</code></a>&nbsp;— 或者任何这些对象的组合。这是 UTF-8 编码的文件内容。</dd>\n <dt id=\"name\"><em>name</em></dt>\n <dd><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_9094f63a1f7efd350dd69d6a8ae174fb\"><code>USVString</code></a>，表示文件名称，或者文件路径。</dd>\n <dt id=\"options\"><em>options</em> <span class=\"badge inline optional\">可选</span></dt>\n <dd>选项对象，包含文件的可选属性。可用的选项如下：\n <ul>\n  <li><code>type</code>: <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a>，表示将要放到文件中的内容的 MIME 类型。默认值为 <code>\"\"</code>&nbsp;。</li>\n  <li><code>lastModified</code>: 数值，表示文件最后修改时间的 Unix 时间戳（毫秒）。默认值为 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/now\"><code>Date.now()</code></a>。</li>\n </ul>\n </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> file <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">File</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">\"foo\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"foo.txt\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">type</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"text/plain\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://w3c.github.io/FileAPI/#file-constructor","title":"File API"}],"query":"api.File.File"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.File.File","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/File/File/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"另见","title":"另见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FileReader\"><code>FileReader</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Blob\"><code>Blob</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"另见","id":"另见"}],"summary":"File() 构造器创建新的 File 对象实例。","popularity":0.0008,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"File()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"File()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"File()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"File.File()","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"File.File()","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/file/file","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/file/file/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/File","title":"File"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/File/File","title":"File.File()"}],"pageTitle":"File.File() - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}